RT @zackwhittaker: New: An ongoing outage at Garmin was caused by ransomware, according to two sources with direct knowledge of the incident. 

WastedLocker, a ransomware strain used by a notorious Russian hacking group — sanctioned by the US Treasury — is likely to blame.
